The main purpose of the scripts within this folder is to make unit tests of all changes related to nomad-extip-manager bash block. Results expected explained in each script.

We need to run the tests under a "scripts" folder which make them all see each other.

For example:

docker run -it --name test_nomad_extip_manager --privileged -v "C:\Folder\Which\Stores\Scripts:/scripts" ubuntu:latest bash